Sentencas: The authers have established a new design for tubular type Solid Oxide Fuel Cells at substantially lower cost with high power density, based on a porous metallic tubular substrate produced by flame coating.
Titulo: New tubular type SOFC using metallic system components

Sentencas: The electrolyte layer is prepared by atmospheric plasma spray coating and densified by surface treatment with inexpensive chemical densification.
Titulo: New tubular type SOFC using metallic system components
